		<title>12TOURISM</title>
		<content>{Hotel:}The Spa Hotel comprises of two 
 large buildings.The annexe (formerly  
 the vicarage) is known as Spa         
 Villa.250 guests can be accomodated   
 and they come mainly from the         
 north-east.                           
    There is a resident Entertainment  
 Officer,and amenities include one of  
 the finest dance floors in the        
 north.Tea dances have recently been   
 introduced to cater for day visitors. 
                                       
 Trips to Scotland,the English lakes   
 and local market towns are organised. 
                                       
{Holiday Accomodation:}One farm taking 
 Bed and Breakfast.                    
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
